title: 3 and Out - Draft Week Kickoff
itunes:title: 3 and Out - Draft Week Kickoff
description:
John kicks off draft week by looking at what appears to be a weak draft, how some teams get into their own heads at the last minute, if any QB’s are worth a first rounder, and why the best GM’s understand value.

Follow John and The Volume on Twitter, Instagram and YouTube for the latest content and updates and check out FanDuel for the best wagering and daily fantasy action! #herd
